markdownRemark.html: An excellent account of the way an author could use a personal device and combine or confuse it with that of a publisher or publishers is now available in the essay of Giorgio Masi, "Simboli e vicende tipografiche doniaine (1546-1549)," in Dissonanze concordi, temi, questioni e personaggi intorno ad Anton Francesco Doni, Bologna, Il Mulino, 2013, pp. 71-98.
